{"tid":1722313,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"台灣暫停三款華為手機銷售 因時區設定有損尊嚴","createTime":"2019-11-15T00:52:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T02:27:26.000Z","uid":144372,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6826b8f29038a4c36b4e5b7fcf01fab53072cc60","tid":1722313,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T00:52:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/台灣暫停三款華為手機銷售-因時區設定有損尊嚴-070903921.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E4%B8%89%E6%AC%BE%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E9%8A%B7%E5%94%AE-%E5%9B%A0%E6%99%82%E5%8D%80%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A%E6%9C%89%E6%90%8D%E5%B0%8A%E5%9A%B4-070903921.html&d=KYS9j8ljDCWJrVyje8%2BOjfzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=1f0efc33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/台灣暫停三款華為手機銷售-因時區設定有損尊嚴-070903921.html</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣暫停內地電訊設備生產商華為三款手機的銷售，指手機內的時區選擇，把台灣顯示為「台灣.中國」。<br />\n台灣通訊傳播委員會在網頁表示，鑒於近日有網絡消息指出，部分手機之通訊錄、時區等關於「台灣」的標示，有與事實不符，甚或有損台灣尊嚴的情況，委員會已即採嚴正措施，要求生產業儘快回復原有標示，並由即日起，手機及平板等產品，申請認證時有關「台灣」標示之設定須正確顯示，否則將撤銷相關的認證。<br />\n當地代理表示，將與華為商討。"},{"pid":"9c48cb575906e8592d703d96ef2e2a27bcc61d4a","tid":1722313,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T00:55:03.000Z","msg":"直接禁左華為啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa914c6cd21598f7417fbff27bc19ef840e581fb","tid":1722313,"uid":9050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T00:57:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d1doTe8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd1doTe8.png&h=7fe617c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁iphone呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能台灣版無問題"},{"pid":"e67a27df7284fd202b06a9703e56e7addf6cf927","tid":1722313,"uid":686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c48cb575906e8592d703d96ef2e2a27bcc61d4a","tid":1722313,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dis